item.title: list
item.description: cdsctl worker list List CDS workers Synopsis List CDS workers cdsctl worker list [flags] Options --fields string Only display specified object fields. 'empty' will display all fields, 'all' will display all object fields, 'field1,field2' to select multiple fields --filter string Filter output based on conditions provided --format string Output format: table|json|yaml (default "table") -h, --help help for list -q, --quiet Only display object's key Options inherited from parent commands -f, --file string set configuration file -k, --insecure (SSL) This option explicitly allows curl to perform "insecure" SSL connections and transfers.
